  "text": "There are several approaches for modeling the distribution of low-level features extracted from images irrespective of their absolute or relative locations within the image. As described above, we investigate three different encoding methods (BOF, FV, and VLAD) for lobulation detection task. We used the VLFeat open source library to implement these encoding methods [CITATION_1] .",
